"Growing pressures to enable and support the use of smartphones, tablets and other personal devices in the workplace means that ignoring the need to put in place some form of Bring Your Own Device (BYOD) policy is no longer an option for today's businesses. More and more organisations now recognise that collaboration is central to the establishment of an effective, agile and flexible environment that can deliver tangible benefits to the business, its staff and customers. Andrew Millard of Citrix outlines a best-practice environment for achieving this."
